description: Record to support submission of GeneRIFs for a gene not in Gene (Bacillus extorquens; Flavobacterium extorquens; Methylobacterium chloromethanicum; Methylobacterium dichloromethanicum; Methylobacterium extorquens; Protomonas extorquens; Pseudomonas extorquens; Vibrio extorquens.  Use when strain, subtype, isolate, etc. is unspecified, or when different from all specified ones in Gene.).
